videos.description: Jack Gibbs made Three Point Jumper as Davidson takes a 3-2 lead
videos.headline: Gibbs 3 gives Davidson early lead

videos.description: Frank Mason III leads Udoka Azubuike for the power alley oop Dunk
videos.headline: Azubuike finishes alley oop from Frank Mason III with the jam

videos.description: Josh Jackson rips down the rebound and makes acrobatic layup as Kansas increases lead to 19-14
videos.headline: Jackson grabs offensive rebound and finishes with layup

videos.description: Oskar Michelsen makes the layup and-1
videos.headline: Davidson's Michelsen runs back door cut to perfection

videos.description: Jack Gibbs hits the Three Point Jumper and the foul as Davidson ties it at 33
videos.headline: Davidson hanging tough as Gibbs hits the 3 and-1

videos.headline: Davidson takes the lead on Aldridge 3

videos.description: Nathan Ekwu makes the running hook just before the halftime buzzer to give Davidson 43-42 halftime lead

videos.headline: Aldridge 3 extends Davidson's 2nd half lead
